a part of a core constant expression. <strong>However, the argument value <code>false</code> exists such that <code>f(false)</code> is a part of a core constant expression.</strong> What's the problem?</p>\n", "PostTypeId": "1", "LastEditorUserId": "5645940", "Id": "45025808", "Score": "1", "OwnerUserId": "5645940", "Tags": "<c++><c++11><language-lawyer>", "AnswerCount": "1"}});